{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841417336,"sessionID":"ses_2879ab85effeNL1ZUUbsvQv248","part":{"id":"prt_d7865973c001ZSMsgy6uWCAUcf","messageID":"msg_d78658bcd001NLyaPdm2xu0qwa","sessionID":"ses_2879ab85effeNL1ZUUbsvQv248","type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"toolu_a671fe1e091b4c28b74b601e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"workloadmanager"},"output":"Found 62 matches\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.sdd_prompt.md:\n  Line 4: Module: pkg/workloadmanager\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md:\n  Line 5: Implement an HTTP service framework in `pkg/workloadmanager` that exposes RESTful APIs for managing AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter Kubernetes resources. The service integrates with the `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` library to provide CRUD operations and watch functionality.\n  Line 66: pkg/workloadmanager/\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md:\n  Line 5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the WorkloadManager HTTP service framework in `pkg/workloadmanager`.\n  Line 10: - **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n  Line 20: - **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/workloadmanager`\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md:\n  Line 8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n  Line 569: pkg/workloadmanager/\n  Line 580: pkg/workloadmanager/\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/ci-cd/design.md:\n  Line 55: - `make docker-build` → default `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE` **`workloadmanager:latest`**\n  Line 67: | Workload manager image | `repository=workloadmanager`, `tag=latest` |\n  Line 85: - Workload manager: `kub